  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nNote: This should be done after merging https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/6508\r\n\r\n`MessageView` (which internally uses `StatusMessage`) with `placeholderMessage: true` should be used for message preview, just as it's done in `AppearanceView`. Currently several old components are used for that, which leads to code duplication.\r\n\r\nAfter that, these components should be deleted:\r\n* `ChatTextView`\r\n* `UsernameLabel`\r\n* `ChatTimePanel`\r\n* `RectangleCorner`\r\n\r\nAnd also `editLabel` can be then removed from `Constants.qml`",
